{"tid":250803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[IT已死]完全冇Lihkg仔理！ExtraTorrent宣布永久關站","createTime":"2017-05-20T11:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T12:58:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f11901608a6facc5128115f0bf48433faf265fc","tid":250803,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/114305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F114305&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7b25a419\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/114305</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nExtraTorrent為全球第二大Torrent網站，為軟體或娛樂內容的線上索引網站，使用者可上傳及下載種子檔案，僅次於The Pirate Bay，周三該站無預警宣佈永久關站。<br />\n<br />\n排名全球第二大的Torrent網站ExtraTorrent在本周三（5/17）無預警地宣布永遠關站了。<br />\n<br />\nExtraTorrent關閉了所有的鏡像網站，<a href=\"http://包括extratorrent.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%ACextratorrent.cc&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=1eb2670c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">包括extratorrent.cc</a>、extra.to及extratorrent.one等，ExtraTorrent並未說明關站原因，只說他們移除了所有的資料，也提醒使用者遠離那些假借ExtraTorrent名義的網站。<br />\n<br />\nExtraTorrent為軟體或娛樂內容的線上索引網站，提供使用者上傳及下載種子檔案，原為全球第二大的Torrent網站，僅次於The Pirate Bay，由於這類的網站通常充斥著盜版內容，因此經常遭到執法機構的取締。<br />\n<br />\n經營ExtraTorrent的SaM在遭到熟識的媒體詢問時，證實了該站將永遠結束，僅說了句「說再見的時候到了」，也未提供更詳細的原因。"},{"pid":"2ab7b8d5a53e91310eaa768eebb536d20a450519","tid":250803,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"已經幾日，連隔離廢登班廢老都有講，反而Lihkg冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03f3ad04bad27fd7da581d8094970e05ab3dc45","tid":250803,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\